underlying_goal: User wanted to sync their local git branch with the remote, pushing their changes while incorporating upstream updates.
primary_success: Successfully and autonomously handled a complex git synchronization task, including stashing local changes, pulling with rebase, pushing, and restoring the stash.
brief_summary: User initiated a git sync command. Claude identified an unstaged local change, stashed it, pulled remote updates with a rebase, pushed the local commit, and then restored the stashed change, completing the full workflow autonomously.
